title: Show HN: AWS Pricing Add-On for Google Sheets
text:
As part of our larger effort at Strake (https://getstrake.com) to make cloud cost problems more tractable for the people that can actually solve them, software devs, we're launching a Google Sheets add-on that lets you include AWS pricing in your formulas.

The add-on is a new version of the open source project originally created by Mike Heffner (https://github.com/mheffner) and we've taken it over with his blessing. The new version is also open source, see: https://github.com/getstrake/aws-pricing-sheets-addon

This is a soft launch and we'd love some feedback. Our goal is to support more AWS services soon and more clouds in the future. We hope it makes life just a little bit easier when tackling your cloud spend.
